## Adding a Skill

1. Create a directory: `{%systemDir%}/skills/{skill-name}/`
2. Add a `SKILL.md` file with frontmatter and procedures
3. Register it in this file
4. Reference the trigger phrase in `{%governanceFile%}` if needed
